Starving down here, you know? Supposed to get food every other week, but you know how it is.

Listen, d'you have any linmetal ore? I can't patch up arms or armor without it. I'll pay you above market rates!
Oh, this is plenty to tide us over 'til the supplies get here. Last load never even showed up! Thanks again.
Any linmetal ore yet? I'll go crazy if that hole in Cafnil's greaves gets any bigger!
